as.*
    Polynomial expansion of the angular sensitivity curve in increasing degress of cosine(zenith)
    [:1] normalization constant of angular sensitivity
    [1:] polynomial expansion coefficients in increasing degree
    --> as.uniform describes a flat / uniform acceptance in 4pi

*spectrum*.txt
    Spectrum of described flasher / LED.
    [:,0] wavelength in nanometer
    [:,1] normalized emission intensity
    --> flasher_laser_532nm_emission_spectrum_datasheet.txt describes a typical 532nm LED
    --> flasher_led_532nm_emission_spectrum_datasheet.txt describes a typical 532nm Nd:YAG laser

